<![CDATA[ 
	<p><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #333333"><strong>中小投资者（散户）最应该向谁学习?</strong><br />---------------------------------------------</span><br /></span></p><p><span><span style="font-size: medium">&mdash;&mdash;兼论沃伦&middot;巴菲特与彼得&middot;林奇之投资区别与联系</span></span></p><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></span> <p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">1．<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span>两人都是全球最成功的投资人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">2．<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span>两人都注意发现成长性的公司</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">（1）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span>巴菲特</span><span>只关心三类公司：一有垄段性资源，二是有差异性，三是有核心竞争力的公司。第三类公司最难寻找。他</span><span>主要侧重于人们生活必须之成长性，如可口可乐、华盛顿邮报和中石油等，一旦认准，长期持有</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">（2）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span>彼得&middot;林奇主要侧重于发现身边、或可能处于萌芽将冒尖之企业，一旦成长则有数倍数十倍收益</span></span></p><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></span> <p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">3．<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span>两人投资公司数量大大不同</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">（1）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span>巴菲特持有的公司数量不多，屈指可数，多是耳熟能详的大公司</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">（2）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span>彼得&middot;林奇投资有</span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">1400</span></span><span>家企业，其他的不至于全赔了，保本的可能性还是很大的，但是只要有十分之一有暴发性成长，则赚大了；真正给他带来财富的，多是&ldquo;黑马&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;在看似没有机会的股票中找到；虽然他投资了</span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">1400</span></span><span>家公司，你能说出几个来吗，呵呵，你说不出来的</span></span></p><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></span> <p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">4．<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span>巴菲特是典型的机构投资人，他是<span>全球机构投资者导师</span>；而</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: medium"><span><span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman">5．<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span>彼得&middot;林奇是典型的个人投资者，他是<span>全世界散户导师</span></span></span></p>
